Class TermISATypeOFRelationship

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TermISATypeOFRelationship extends OMRSLine
TermISATypeOFRelationship is a relationships between an entity of type GlossaryTerm and an entity of type GlossaryTerm. The ends of the relationships are stored as entity proxies, where there is a 'proxy' name by which the entity type is known. The first entity proxy has supertypes as the proxy name for entity type GlossaryTerm. The second entity proxy has subtypes as the proxy name for entity type GlossaryTerm. Each entity proxy also stores the entities guid. Defines an inheritance relationship between two spine objects.
